oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Welcome Fairmen (Suite)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Twitty, Conway; Craddock, Billy; Smith, Cal; Lynn, Loretta; James, Sonny; Grandpa Jones, 1913-1998; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color half sheet (red and black on white) announcing Variety Attractions Country and Western entertainment with Conway Twitty, Cal Smith, Crash Craddock, Loretta Lynn, Sonny James, Crystal Gayle, Grandpa Jones and Jeannie Riley in Zanesville, Ohio. Poster features metal photoplates of Conway Twitty, Cal Smith, Crash Craddock, Loretta Lynn, Sonny James, Crystal Gayle, Grandpa Jones and Jeannie Riley. Poster order 17208. To view the paperwork associated with this poster, see https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/21124.
